+    "en": "<p>For Media Servers installed with Docker Compose, <a href='https://help.cardinalapps.io/guides/cardinal-media-server/uninstall' target='_blank'>reinstalling with Docker Compose</a> is recommended instead of using this built-in utility.</p><p>A factory reset will deindex your media, remove any other data, and return your Media Server to its initial state. Your cloud account will be unlinked from this Media Server.</p><p>Your Media Server will become unresponsive while this process runs (it can take a while).</p>"
